  "original_title": "\u0dba\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dca 5 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0db3\u0dd4 \u0dbb\u0da7\u0d9a \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dd1\u0db8\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dba\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Yuan Wang 5 should not be influenced by any country",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "China maintains that the Yuan Wang-5 Chinese scientific research vessel will not affect the security and economic interests of any country and should not be interfered with by a third party.",
        "Chinese Foreign Ministry Spokesperson Mr. Wang Wenbin said this while answering a question raised by a journalist at a press conference held today (16) in Beijing.",
        "Mr. Wang Wenbin said here that the Chinese scientific research ship Yuan Wang-5 successfully docked at Hambantota Port with the active cooperation of the Sri Lankan side on the afternoon of the 16th Beijing time.",
        "China and Sri Lanka, as two traditional friendly countries, have maintained close cooperation in the field of marine science research for a long time.",
        "He also said that the marine science research activities carried out by the Yuan Wang-5 scientific research ship are in accordance with international rules and regulations and will not affect the security and economic benefits of any country, and should not be interfered with by third parties."
      ],
